rt\n- Pinia / client helpers\n- documentation and playground\n\n### Nuxt module details\n\n- built with `defineNuxtModule`\n- explicit `configKey`\n- explicit `compatibility.nuxt`\n- TypeScript + ESM\n- published on npm\n- docs available\n- playground/demo available in the repository\n\n### Why I think it fits the module list\n\nThe module is intended as a reusable third-party Nuxt module for teams building backend-first Nuxt applications with FeathersJS.\n\nIt is already packaged and documented for public use, and I would like to improve its discoverability in the Nuxt ecosystem.\n\n### Notes\n\nI am **not** requesting transfer to `nuxt-modules` / `@nuxtjs` at this stage.  \nThe immediate goal is only to request **community listing** on `nuxt.com/modules`.\n\nIf you think something should still be improved before listing, I’m happy to adjust the package metadata or documentation.\n\nThank you!\n\n\n### Repository\n\nhttps://github.com/vevedh/nuxt-feathers-zod\n\n### npm\n\nhttps://www.npmjs.com/package/nuxt-feathers-zod\n\n### Nuxt Compatibility\n\nNuxt 4","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nuxt/modules/issues/1455/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nuxt/modules/issues/1455/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"duplicate","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/waaseyaa/framework/issues/1411","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/waaseyaa/framework","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/waaseyaa/framework/issues/1411/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/waaseyaa/framework/issues/1411/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/waaseyaa/framework/issues/1411/events","html_url":"https://github.com/waaseyaa/framework/issues/1411","id":4417182055,"node_id":"I_kwDORa46qs8AAAABB0jZZw","number":1411,"title":"[admin-spa] Mission M1: Dependency + too